                    _beforeSP.poolData[i].totalDepositAssets +
                        _beforeSP.assetDeposits[i] +
                        _beforeSP.pendingInterest[i],
                    "SP-03: SuperPool.deposit() must credit the correct number of assets to the pools in depositQueue"
